column4: RT @Georgetown This month, Health Education Services and partners will host a number of events across campus for #SexualAssaultAwarenessMonth. We'd like to remind students during #SAAM that resources and support services are available at: https://t.co/j8rBoTFc6l https://t.co/OdHqQ77SNq
